data.description: Ranch style home with a large fenced in yard. Walk into this home and you will notice the hardwood floors and large roomsFormal Dinning room. Kitchen has lots of cabinets  and all the appliances remain. Sunroom in the back of home has wrap around windows. Sit and enjoy the most beautiful large oak tree in the back yard. Full Unfinished basement with room to make it your own. Lots of space for storage and great to add more living space.Washer and dryer will remain.
